<view class="container">
	<swiper current="{{currentIndex}}" bindchange="swiperChange"
	style="width；100%;height:{{contentHeight}}px" indicator-dots="{{true}}" autoplay="{{true}}" circular="{{true}}" interval="{{10000}}" duration="{{500}}" vertical="{{true}}">
		<!-- 人人分利 -->
		<swiper-item>
			<view class="share-firend" style="background-image: url(http://7xu5hi.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/201805051351037959319.png);background-size:100% 100%">
			</view>
			<view class="share-content">
				<view class="share-box">
					<image class="share-person" src="../../images/person.png"></image>
					<view class="share-qrcode font-12">
						<view class="qrcode-white">
							<canvas class='qrcode' canvas-id='canvas'></canvas>
						</view>
						<view style="margin-top: 10rpx"><text>快去让好友扫描二维码</text></view>
						<view><text>赢取现金奖励吧</text></view>
					</view>
					<view class="share-rule">
						<image class="share-rule-img" src="../../images/rule.png"></image>
						<view class="share-rule-text">
							<text>当你邀请的好友在马管家平台注册及消费时,你可以获得返现。返现金额为返现比例乘以你好友的消费金额,不同时段返现比例可能不同,返现规则最终解释权归马管家所有</text>
						</view>
					</view>
				</view>
			</view>
		</swiper-item>
		<!-- 邀请红包 -->
		<swiper-item style="position:relative">
			<image src="../../images/yaoqinghonbaobg.jpg" style="width:100%;height:{{contentHeight}}px;" />
			<view style="position:absolute;width:80%;left:10%;bottom:40rpx;background:white;box-shadow:0 0 10px 4px rgba(184,42,66,.75);padding:20rpx;" class="border-radius5">
				<view style="font-size:32rpx;color:#222;padding:20rpx 40rpx;" class="flex flex-row-center">
					<text class="line"></text>
					<text style="padding:0 20rpx;">活动规则</text>
					<text class="line"></text>
				</view>
				<view style="font-size:26rpx;line-height:2;color:#666;">
					<view>1) 将外卖或者团购商家店铺分享给好友；</view>
					<view>2) 您的好友通过您分享的链接成功下单并完成订单时， 您可以获得返现；</view>
					<view>3) 返现金额为返现比例乘以您好友的消费金额，不同时段返现比例可能不同；</view>
					<view>4) 返现规则最终解释权归马管家所有。</view>
				</view>
				<view style="text-align:center;padding:40rpx 20rpx;" catch:tap="gotoIndexTap">
					<image src="../../images/getMoneyBtn.png" style="width:500rpx;height:80rpx;"/>
				</view>
			</view>
		</swiper-item>
	</swiper>


	
</view>